quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  79,27,Koo! Nobutinyu okhuloonga enywe nohomba likulu? Ye niye waliumbakha
  79,28,"yalichingula, nalikasia obulayi"
  79,29,"Ne nara eshilima mushilo shiayio, ne nayiniamwo eshitere"
  79,30,Akhurula awo nakwalasia liloba
  79,31,Narusiamwo amatsikayio nende emimela
  79,32,Ne nabuusia tsingulu
  79,33,Khubukhala bwenyu nende ibiayo bienyu
  79,34,Olwamatinyu amakhongo kaliula
  79,35,Inyanga yomundu aliitsulila kayakhola
  79,36,ne jahanamu ilisitibwa khu ulola
  79,37,ne ulia waburirira mubufuru
  79,38,mana nachama muno ubulamu bweshialo
  79,39,toto jahanamu neshimenyo shishie
  79,40,"Ne ulia waria okhwema imbeli Wa Nyasaye wuwe , nakaania omwoyo kukwe obwikombi"
  79,41,Toto oyo Mwikulu nishiliba eshimenyo shishie
  79,42,Bakhurebanga ebise bieyindukho biliba lina
  79,43,Oli nashina ewe wakhanyala okhuyirumbula
  79,44,Obumalilishi bweyinyanga eyo buli khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi
  79,45,Toto ewe oli butswa Omwikanyilisi khu ulia owaria inyanga eyo
  79,46,"Olwa baliyilola inyanga eyo, balikaala mbu shibamenya khwo (khushialo) tawe halali ingolobe ndala nohomba eshitere shiayo"